{
  "stem": "15694.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a week or two later, it came up-- you know, it got up and up and up. 100, 150, 200.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The end was 300.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But apparently-- now, the youngsters of this ghetto, we met from time to time in groups.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Unfortunately, we couldn't organize resistance because we had no weapons, and nobody to really lead us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we were talking about it, and regretting it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were calculating if they shoot as many as they do, if the war would-- would last 10 years, there would-- 10% of us would be killed.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Little did we know there was less than 10% that survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And the war didn't last for 10 years, as you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, at one stage, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was asked to work for the Germans in an ammunition camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I got out of it by pretending I had tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I knew all the symptoms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I went to a Polish doctor and got a certificate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But when the time came that they-- we heard that there were transports to the east, which the Germans called resettlement-- now I forgot the-- the German word for it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Doesn't really matter now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Resettlement.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't trust it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But what should we do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, at that time, when the time came nearer-- of course, the Einsatzgruppen, for one reason or another, maybe-- they didn't come to Bochnia.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in January, 1942-- but that is, of course, I only learned later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The famous or rather infamous Wannsee or German Wannsee Conference where 15 people decided [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the fate of the Jews, the final solution.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it wasn't to be by Einsatzgruppen anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was to build extermination camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
